snippet.title: Jottobots for PC!
snippet.description:
http://jottobots.com

Jottobots is a miniature metroidvania action platformer, YEAH!  It was originally made in 2009 for the ARTxGAME collective as a collaboration between Kyle Pulver and J. Otto Seibold.  For the public release it has been spruced up with music, sound, online leaderboards, achievements, and more!  Check it out at http://jottobots.com
